amendment.description: An amendment numbered 76 printed in Part B of House Report 118-269 to prohibit the use of funds to finalize, implement, or enforce the proposed rule entitled "Conflicts of Interest Associated with the Use of Predictive Data Analytics by Broker-Dealers and Investment Advisers".
